result.adr_address: 27 Harbour Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 27 Harbour Rd, Wan Chai, Hong Kong
result.name: Super Super Congee & Noodles

reviews.text: Good food when hot - tea is best.

The congee and rice roll is really very nice and it's a great combination to start your day especially when it's cold. Menu is easy to order with an exception of a few that are not labelled with numbers. Staff serving the food is not very friendly and expects that you understand their muffled voice due to their face mask.
Too expensive for the seniors,  should be half price for those who have senior card. Government will subsidize upon request by your organization.
So far so good.

Not a bad place away from the crowd of main street Wanchai. 

Food is standard fast food, but fairly clean compared with lots of other fast food joints. 

Also, a roomy place that seats many patrons, not the usual back-touching-back experience in some rather dodgy local restaurants. 

Coffee is freshly grinded for those who are picky with their cocoa. 

Try to avoid the 12 to 1 pm time slot though, unless you do not mind being surrounded by construction workers! 😂

result.adr_address: 香港灣仔港灣道25號
result.name: 海港中心

reviews.text: 可以给狗仔玩一流•

海港中心（Harbour Centre）是香港一座寫字樓，位處灣仔港灣道25號，樓高33層，於1983年落成，鄰近香港會議展覽中心、灣仔碼頭等地點。

大樓內集有多個國家的領事館，包括澳洲駐港總領事館、辛巴威駐港總領事館、摩納哥駐港名譽領事館等等，其他租戶包括東方海外貨櫃航運公司，IDP教育有限公司（28樓2807-09室），以及選舉事務處、選舉管理委員會的辦事處等。

海港中心下層設有商場，名為海港中心商場，面積有40,865平方呎。
在香港仔區比較舊式的翻新商場一去無妨
這裡的景色十分美麗，食店多元化。適合明友聚會的好去處
